<li><p>Preview changes:</p>
<ul>
<li>Click the “Preview” button in the top right corner</li>
<li>Or use Command Palette (Ctrl+Shift+P / Cmd+Shift+P) and type “Quarto: Preview”</li>
</ul></li>
</ol>
</section>
